data.description: Welcome home! Enter this beautiful, 2,045 square foot concrete block home through the covered front poch, into the open floor plan with endless options for living, dining and office room options. Home boasts 3 bedrooms plus a bonus room with French doors for home office. Enclosed Florida room has sepearate AC for year round use and comfort. Large deck in backyard overlooks a pond. Very private and peaceful setting. Roof new in 2019, under warranty, termite bond.
